@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kntwta(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.28 + v1 + 0.95)) - (0.89 + wp.cos(v1 + 0.01)))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.abs((v2 + 0.92 + v1 + 0.23)))
    v0 = wp.exp(0.12)
    tmp = v0
    v2 = (wp.abs((v2 + 0.70 + v1 + 0.51)) - ((v0 + 0.36 + v0 + 0.79) * (v2 + 0.48 / v0 + 0.05)))
    data[tid] = v0
